@startuml
title Sequence 03 - Menyimpan Lowongan ke Wishlist
autonumber
actor Mahasiswa
participant "Frontend Portal" as FE
participant "Wishlist/Vacancy API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Mahasiswa -> FE: Klik simpan lowongan
FE -> API: POST /wishlist {vacancy_id}
API -> DB: Cek vacancy aktif
API -> DB: Cek StudentWishlistVacancies unik
alt belum tersimpan
  API -> DB: Insert StudentWishlistVacancies
  DB --> API: Commit OK
  API --> FE: Wishlist tersimpan
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan sukses
else sudah tersimpan / vacancy tidak valid
  API --> FE: 400/404
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan error
end
@enduml
